    },
    "game-id": "f708cec9f502249f5a83e2071db6311b",
    "text": "Executor dragons tend to be aligned with Heaven, but there are some who would consider themselves otherwise. Gods like Sarenrae, Iomedae, and Trudd all have executor dragon allies, acting as either generals in their godly armies, bodyguards, heralds, or as loyal retainers in the gods\u2019 efforts on Golarion. In some instances, executor dragons choose instead to align themselves with the deities who are not of Heaven, but instead have other divine allies. Psychopomps speak of one executor dragon that serves Urgathoa as both bodyguard and pet, gorging itself at the endless feasts that Urgathoa holds nearly daily.",
